OL,3,CHuddersfield railway station to close
OL,4,Cfor a month
OL,6,FA major station on the trans-Pennine
OL,7,Frailway connecting Leeds and
OL,8,FManchester will be closed for a month
OL,9,Ffor engineering work.
OL,11,FRepairs at Huddersfield station, which
OL,12,Fis used by more than 8,000 people a
OL,13,Fday, began more than a year ago as
OL,14,Fpart of the Transpennine Route Upgrade
OL,15,Fproject.
OL,17,FNetwork Rail said the latest phase of
OL,18,Fwork would mean no trains running
OL,19,Fthrough the station between Saturday,
OL,20,F30 August, and Monday, 29 September.
