OL,3,CHuddersfield railway station to close
OL,4,Cfor a month
OL,6,FIt added that "diversionary routes and
OL,7,Frail replacement buses" would be in
OL,8,Foperation, with "Brighouse functioning
OL,9,Fas the gateway to Huddersfield in
OL,10,Fthose weeks".
OL,12,FFollowing the full 30-day closure,
OL,13,Fonly three platforms will operate on a
OL,14,Ftemporary basis.
OL,16,FThe company said it would not release
OL,17,Ffurther information on diversion
OL,18,Froutes until June.
