OL,3,CHuddersfield railway station to close
OL,4,Cfor a month
OL,6,FGareth Hope, who is working on the
OL,7,Fproject, said: "This 30-day closure
OL,8,Fwill allow us to take a giant leap
OL,9,Ftowards giving the station a deserved
OL,10,Fmakeover without harming its heritage.
OL,12,F"Ultimately, the work in Huddersfield
OL,13,Fis key to improving the journeys of
OL,14,Fmillions of people across the north -
OL,15,Fincreasing the number of tracks
OL,16,Fthrough the station and remodelling
OL,17,Fits platforms means we will will be
OL,18,Fable to run faster, more frequent
OL,19,Ftrains with enhanced capacity in the
OL,20,Ffuture."
