OL,3,CHuddersfield railway station to close
OL,4,Cfor a month
OL,6,FThe latest work includes major track
OL,7,Fand platform remodelling to allow
OL,8,Fmore, larger trains to run through the
OL,9,Farea "on a greener, more reliable
OL,10,Frailway".
OL,12,FThe station's roof canopy is also
OL,13,Fbeing restored, although the
OL,14,Fscaffolding and coverings of one
OL,15,Fsection will be removed in the coming
OL,16,Fweeks.
OL,18,FA new footbridge is set be installed
OL,19,Fin the station and the historic Grade
OL,20,FII listed tearooms will be restored.
